{"tid":1757011,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【區選贏咗就做嘢啦】本區被失蹤人士關注組","createTime":"2019-11-26T10:02:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-27T09:12:08.000Z","uid":300554,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"540255d5d14486e8bf713a26813caf4e5864e58d","tid":1757011,"uid":300554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T10:02:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7wmrS0A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7wmrS0A.jpg&h=d5b4994e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n喱啲無消息嘅消息難以fc最為恐怖<br />\n累積幾千被捕嘅有義務律師團跟緊<br />\n但數唔清嘅失蹤人士呢？<br />\n區議會係咪應該就喱啲問題開個本區關注組？<br />\n見到有傳出事嘅係本區嘅，就出動去關注當事人<br />\n重要喺流言泛濫嘅網絡世界交代返已有跟進<br />\n保護手足，保護大家<br />\n<br />\n仲有各種相關事務 既課緊人力物力落抗爭 同時亦係對本區社區建設嘅實務 相信區選有唔少新血係因抗爭而推動到參選兼得選 好好利用社會俾你嘅權力去做返啲嘢 宜家你可以做到嘅嘢有好多！勿忘初衷 齊上齊落啊！<br />\n<br />\n區選贏咗 無嘢好慶祝 做嘢啦唔該<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/78603354_151145202906473_4201509950100340736_n.jpg?_nc_cat=104&amp;_nc_ohc=P61cPpFPcGQAQngxFwjvrlFaGPQdOO4JsR9BIMoCek0Kx91zIKMcJkr4g&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-1.fna&amp;oh=4bc38c19e426c2f499c0cc27383efd4a&amp;oe=5E8033FF\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F78603354_151145202906473_4201509950100340736_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D104%26_nc_ohc%3DP61cPpFPcGQAQngxFwjvrlFaGPQdOO4JsR9BIMoCek0Kx91zIKMcJkr4g%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-1.fna%26oh%3D4bc38c19e426c2f499c0cc27383efd4a%26oe%3D5E8033FF&h=b1dda3a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n推到所有區議會凝聚本區抗爭力量"},{"pid":"c9af1c85eae6744a58d081ad34556298d0befa0d","tid":1757011,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T10:04:22.000Z","msg":"Twitter 戰線勿鬆懈！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1756092\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1756092</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n請幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">出門之前 rt like reply</span><br />\nTwitter組24小時keep住更新<br />\n幫